::Proto::

"Wait up!" Proto yells, taking a few steps after Stranato, "I need to assign 
you-AH!" Proto trips over his own feet, falling face first to the ground.

"Quarters," he finishes, getting to his feet. He activates his comm, sending 
a transmission to Stranato: "When you're done fighting, come back and I'll 
assign you quarters."

Proto turns around, heading back into the Cybertronian Fire.
